title: Ask HN: Did GitHub reset your account password and revoked all of your PAT?
text: Seems that many users got an email informing them that: "We’re writing to let you know that we observed suspicious activity that suggests a threat actor used a Personal Access Token (PAT) associated with your account to access private repository metadata."
